formulas.formula: ( soc_pct_gemcar*gemcar_cst_all + soc_pct_gemcis*gemcis_cst_all + soc_pct_paccar*paccar_cst_all + soc_pct_paccis*paccis_cst_all + soc_pct_doccar*doccar_cst_all + soc_pct_doccis*doccis_cst_all + soc_pct_vincar*vincar_cst_all + soc_pct_vincis*vincis_cst_all + soc_pct_pmtcar*pmtcar_cst_all + soc_pct_pmtcis*pmtcis_cst_all) * (1/soc_pct_all)
